ized code-base PICASO, we have added these\noriginal features as well as the new capability of self-consistently treating\ndisequilibrium chemistry. This code is widely applicable to Hydrogen-dominated\natmospheres (e.g., brown dwarfs and giant planets).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Aug 2022 16:37:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-18"}
