 to put an upper bound of\norder PeV on the masses of scalar superpartners.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Aug 2022 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 May 2023 18:43:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-24"}
