an makespan reduction of 7.18% and 18.01% assuming a\nmean task runtime prediction error of 15%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Aug 2022 18:47:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Oct 2022 10:11:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-18"}
