ially modulated Hadronic layers and tubes. The comparison of\nthe present approach both with the instantons-dyons liquid approach and with\nLattice QCD is shortly outlined.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Aug 2022 19:45:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Oct 2022 14:01:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-27"}
