ependent parameters (e.g. NV conversion efficiency) are held\nconstant, we find that shallower NV layers should yield the best SNR, which is\nconsistent with experimental findings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Aug 2022 21:26:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Dec 2022 19:54:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-22"}
