nt f_{i} \\, d \\mu_{\\beta_i}\n\\cdot \\int f_{k+1} \\, d \\mu_G \\quad \\text{in } L^{2}(\\lambda). \\end{split}\n\\end{equation*}\n  We also study the phenomenon of joint mixing. Among other things we establish\njoint mixing for skew tent maps and for restrictions of finite Blaschke\nproducts to the unit circle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Aug 2022 04:12:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-31"}
