 is more effective than current approaches. We\nconclude by shedding light on the challenges and opportunities in multimodal\nunderstanding of educational presentations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Aug 2022 05:30:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-18"}
